  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Prerequisites: Dragonborn</em></p><p>When angered, you radiate menace. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li>Increase your Strength, Constitution, or Charisma by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li><li>Instead of exhaling destructive energy, you can expend a use of your Breath Weapon trait to roar, forcing each creature of your choice within 30 feet of you to make a Wisdom saving throw (DC 8 + your proficiency bonus + your Charisma modifier). A target automatically succeeds on the save if it can't hear or see you. On a failed save, a target becomes frightened of you for 1 minute. If the frightened target takes any damage, it can repeat the saving throw, ending the effect on itself on a success.</li></ul>",
